				          <h1 id="page-title" class="page-title">Home</h1>
				      		<div id="page-description" class="page-description"><p>Disability Rights Connecticut, Inc. (DRCT) is an independent, statewide non-profit disability advocacy organization that advocates for the civil and human rights of individuals with disabilities in Connecticut.&nbsp;</p></div>
