<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">Help Us Reach Our Goal</h2><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>Your Donation</strong> accelerates positive change for people with disabilities. <br><strong>Your Donation</strong> ensures that DRCT's advocacy can have a systems-wide impact to ensure that policies, regulations, and legislation that impact the needs of people with disabilities are addressed.<br><strong>Your Donation</strong> will help DRCT achieve its goal of raising <span style="text-decoration:underline">$25,000</span> to continue advocating for people with disabilities. </p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><strong>We are grateful for your support.</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Deborah Dorfman, Executive Director/Attorney</p>
