<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">Yale Students, Alumni Reach Settlement Agreement to Resolve Lawsuit Against <br>Yale University</h1><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>Elis for Rachael, Inc., two Yale students, and Yale University release the following joint statement:</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>"The parties have reached a settlement agreement to resolve a lawsuit filed last November in federal district court related to policies and practices impacting students with mental health disabilities."&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>For more information, please visit&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://www.elisforrachael.org/" target="_blank"><strong>www.elisforrachael.org</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://www.bazelon.org/" target="_blank"><strong>www.bazelon.org</strong></a><strong>, or&nbsp;</strong><a href="https://www.disrightsct.org/" target="_blank"><strong>www.disrightsct.org</strong></a><strong>.</strong>&nbsp;</p>
</div>




















  
  



