  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Open and Affirming Statement:</p><p style="margin-left:40px;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Disability Rights Connecticut </p><p style="margin-left:40px;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">welcomes all people </p><p style="margin-left:40px;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">with disabilities. </p>
